<header class="modal-header">
    <h1>你确定你要删除这个帖子?</h1>
</header>
<a class="close icon-x" href="" title="Close" {{action "closeModal"}}><span class="hidden">Close</span></a>

<div class="modal-body">
    <p>
        您即将删除 "<strong>{{post.title}}</strong>".<br />
        这是永久的！ 无备份，无还原，无魔术还原按钮.<br />
        我们警告你，好吗？
    </p>
</div>

<div class="modal-footer">
    <button {{action "closeModal"}} class="btn btn-default btn-minor">取消</button>
    {{#gh-spin-button action="confirm" class="btn btn-red" submitting=submitting}}删除{{/gh-spin-button}}
</div>
